        "chapter": 57,
        "line_start": 280,
        "line_end": 284,
        "text": "我简直做梦也想不到你会离开恶人谷"
      },
      {
        "chapter": 59,
        "line_start": 28,
        "line_end": 28,
        "text": "恶人谷里，究竟发生了什么大事？"
      },
      {
        "chapter": 63,
        "line_start": 274,
        "line_end": 274,
        "text": "恶人谷"
      },
      {
        "chapter": 122,
        "line_start": 306,
        "line_end": 306,
        "text": "他们在'恶人谷'受了二十年活罪后"
